Software Used
</h2>

<div class="course-card">

<h3>
Autodesk Fusion 360
</h3>

<p>

Fusion 360 was used throughout the course to design, prototype, and improve competition solutions before they were built. By this point, CAD had become second nature and allowed my team to quickly iterate ideas under competition deadlines.

</p>

