<section id="projects">

<span class="section-tag">
PROJECTS
</span>

<h2>
QCESC High School Tech Challenge
</h2>

<div class="project-grid">

<div class="project">

<img src="/images/problems/bridges.jpg">

<h3>Battle of the Bridges</h3>

<p>

Designed and tested a bridge to maximize strength while minimizing material. Our team placed <strong>4th Overall</strong>, making this the most technically challenging event of the competition. Was unable to physically attend due to FRC Competition

</p>

</div>

<div class="project">

<img src="/images/problems/trebuchet.jpg">

<h3>Trebuchet Egg Toss ⭐</h3>

<p>

My favorite event! We designed, built, and optimized a trebuchet capable of launching an egg accurately over long distances. Our team finished <strong>3rd Place</strong>.

</p>

</div>

<div class="project">

<img src="/images/problems/boat.jpg">

<h3>Cardboard Boat Regatta</h3>

<p>

Build a boat entirely from cardboard... then race it across the water.

Official Result: <strong>DNF (Did Not Finish )</strong>

Still one of the funniest engineering experiences I've ever had.

</p>

</div>

</div>

